**[AUU QR Code Generator](https://qr.auufree.com/)** is a high-performance, privacy-focused online tool to create stunning QR codes. Whether for business or personal use, you can design professional QR codes in seconds.

Visit the App: **[https://qr.auufree.com/](https://qr.auufree.com/)**

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 **Full Customization**: Adjust foreground/background colors, gradients, and corner styles.
- 🖼️ **Logo Integration**: Upload and embed your brand logo into the QR code easily.
- 📏 **High-Quality Export**: Supports PNG, JPG, and **SVG (Vector)** for high-quality printing.
- 🔒 **Privacy First**: All processing is done locally in your browser. No data is sent to our server.
- 📱 **Mobile Friendly**: Fully responsive design for seamless use on any device.

## 🛠️ Technical Stack

- **Framework**: React / Vite
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Rendering**: HTML5 Canvas & SVG API

## 🚀 Quick Start (Local Development)

```bash
git clone [https://github.com/your-username/your-repo.git](https://github.com/your-username/your-repo.git)
cd your-repo
npm install
npm run dev
